    "en": {
      "title": "Three people who attacked three people, including Deshbandu, were caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that three suspects were arrested for assaulting and injuring three police officers, including the Senior DIG in charge of the Western Province, Mr. Deshbandu Tennakoon, on May 10 in the Kollupitiya police domain.",
        "Police say they are residents of Colombo 15 and Pitabaddara.",
        "They are going to be presented to the court under the facts of assaulting the police officers, illegal population and violation of the law."
      ],
